title: Cafe Colonial
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional American fare such as burgers, fries, onion rings, and salads. Has a separate vegan menu which includes burgers (with Amy's brand black bean burger), fry bread tacos, mini-pizza, and vegan mozzerella fries. The vegan BBQ sauce is made in-house. At least 1 vegan beer. Occasionally hosts guest chefs, including vegan ones. Live music shows most nights in the main dining room.
